des:
Have you ever wanted to have a handful of Darth Vader facts at your disposal? If you answered "yes" then Vader Facts is for you. Discover interesting info with is unofficial skill about your favorite Sith ranging from character information to behind the scenes facts. 

This skill is in no way associated with the Star Wars franchise or Lucasfilm.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
